query:
SELECT cp.id, cp.slug, cp.headline, cp.hourlyRate, u.name, u.email 
FROM coach_profiles cp 
LEFT JOIN users u ON cp.userId = u.id 
WHERE cp.status = 'approved' AND cp.profileComplete = true 
ORDER BY cp.id;
